---
title: Warm Thai Pumpkin Salad with Peanut Dressing
description: We love thinking outside the box, like using aromatic green curry paste to flavour roasted pumpkin, then adding a creamy peanut dressing to make a warm, satisfying salad. It's the Thai flavours you love, served in a fresh new way!
